EVALUATION AND MEASUREMENT FRAMEWORK\
Evaluation will be structured around four primary metrics:\
1.\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 Housing Stability Index \'96 measuring reduction in eviction rates, rent burden, and turnover among pilot buildings.\
2.\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 Subsidy Conversion Efficiency \'96 tracking the fiscal differential between rental support and ownership investment.\
3.\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0 Ownership Equity Accrual \'96 analyzing share value, capital reserves, and unit improvements over time.\
